install netplan and config the file called 00-installer-config.yaml
Add PTR recourd to dns 
adduser name sudo and disaple remote root ssh
run install docker on ubunto and check the status.
use docker run to print hello world 
run sudo install docker-compose --version to see the version 
run sudo docker run --rm archlinux:latest /bin/echo "Hello world"
run docker images to see the images that i have 
run sudo docker run -it archlinux /bin/uname -a to displayed the comtainer 
run docker run -d -P training/webapp python app.py to pull down the appication that associated with sample pythone web application 
run docker ps to see the docker network
run docker stop "testapp" to stop the test app
